&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Serve as a Senior Technical Advisor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Act as a trusted advisor and subject matter expert on Builder’s platform, helping&amp;nbsp;customers identify high-value use cases, apply best practices, and translate&amp;nbsp;product capabilities into scalable implementation patterns.&lt;/li&gt;
